TWComponent.script: tw.local.sqlStatement select distinct LP."NAME" ApplicationName, LP.SHORT_NAME as ProjectAcronym, LS."NAME" as SnapshotName, LS.IS_ACTIVE as IsActive, LS.IS_DEFAULT as IsDefault, LP.IS_SYSTEM IsSystem, LP.IS_TOOLKIT IsToolkit, LUX.USER_NAME as LastModifiedByUser, LS.LAST_MODIFIED LastModified from LSW_SNAPSHOT LS, LSW_PROJECT LP, LSW_BPD_INSTANCE LBI, LSW_USR_XREF LUX where LS.PROJECT_ID = LP.PROJECT_ID and LBI.SNAPSHOT_ID(+) = LS.SNAPSHOT_ID and LUX.USER_ID = LS.LAST_MODIFIED_BY_USER_ID and LBI.BPD_INSTANCE_ID is null
